PROBLEMS & TROUBLESHOOTING: 
1. To select the right port and type of arduino 
2.To check the loose connections 
3. connection of led display to breadboard should be proper 


PRECAUTIONS: 
1.handle lcd screen carefully

 
OUTCOMES:

